<template>
    <form>
        <v-card class="px-10 py-10">
            <v-menu
                v-model="menu1"
                :close-on-content-click="false"
                max-width="290"
            >
                <template v-slot:activator="{ on, attrs }">
                    <v-text-field
                    :value="computedDateFormattedMomentjs"
                    clearable
                    label="Reporting Date"
                    readonly
                    v-bind="attrs"
                    v-on="on"
                    @click:clear="date = null"
                    ></v-text-field>
                </template>
                <v-date-picker
                    v-model="date"
                    @change="menu1 = false"
                ></v-date-picker>
            </v-menu>
            <v-select
                v-model="select"
                :items="items"
                label="Unit *"
                required
                @change="$v.select.$touch()"
                @blur="$v.select.$touch()"
            ></v-select>
        </v-card>
        <v-row>
            <v-col
                cols="12"
                sm="12"
                md="6"
                lg="6"
            >
                <v-card 
                    class="px-10 py-10"
                >
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="email"
                        :error-messages="emailErrors"
                        label="Maintenace Service"
                        required
                        @input="$v.email.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.email.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="email"
                        :error-messages="emailErrors"
                        label="Maintenace Service"
                        required
                        @input="$v.email.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.email.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="email"
                        :error-messages="emailErrors"
                        label="Complaint About"
                        required
                        @input="$v.email.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.email.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-text-field
                        v-model="email"
                        :error-messages="emailErrors"
                        label="Complaint raised by *"
                        required
                        @input="$v.email.$touch()"
                        @blur="$v.email.$touch()"
                    ></v-text-field>
                </v-card>
            </v-col>
            <v-col
                cols="12"
                sm="12"
                md="6"
                lg="6"
            >
                <v-card 
                    class="px-10 py-10"
                >
                    <v-textarea
                        counter
                        label="Complain details"
                        :rules="rules"
                        :value="value"
                        rows="12"
                    ></v-textarea>
                </v-card>
            </v-col>
        </v-row>
        <v-row 
            class="mt-3"
        >
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
                <v-btn
                    class="mr-4"
                    min-width="150"
                >
                    Clear
                </v-btn>
                <v-btn
                    color="primary"
                    class="mr-4"
                    min-width="150"
                >
                    Preview
                </v-btn>
        </v-row>
    </form>
</template>
<script>
import moment from 'moment'
import { format, parseISO } from 'date-fns'

export default {
    name : 'Complaint',
    data: () => ({
      // https://github.com/date-fns/date-fns/blob/master/docs/upgradeGuide.md#string-arguments
      date: format(parseISO(new Date().toISOString()), 'yyyy-MM-dd'),
      menu1: false,
      menu2: false,
      rules: [v => v.length <= 255 || 'Max 255 characters'],
      value: 'Hello!',
    }),

    computed: {
      computedDateFormattedMomentjs () {
        return this.date ? moment(this.date).format('dddd, MMMM Do YYYY') : ''
      },
      computedDateFormattedDatefns () {
        return this.date ? format(this.date, 'EEEE, MMMM do yyyy') : ''
      },
    },
}
</script>
